cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with video summarization, which is a common task in computer vision. It could also belong to Multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with summarizing a collection of videos. Information Retrieval (cs.IR) is another likely sub-category as the paper discusses extracting informative summaries from videos. Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) are also possible sub-categories as the paper proposes a novel optimization method and explores complementarity within the videos.
